  "title": "Welder & Flame cutter",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to read      the engineering drawings for sheet metal fabrication items and structural      welding.</li>\n  <li>Follow the      welding symbols stated in the drawing to complete the process</li>\n  <li>TIG/MIG/Fiber      laser weld/Spot weld.</li>\n  <li>Welding and      cutting metal parts using gas flame, or an electric arc and other sources      of heat to melt and cut or to melt and fuse metal.</li>\n  <li>Machine      maintenance and work place safety</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements and Qualifications</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Highschool/ITE      or certification course in welding.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Able to work independently</p>",
